    "description": "Continuous testing is a practice that dramatically improves efficiency of unit testing and test driven development. This course provides background on continuous testing and explores the use of a tool called NCrunch to increase development efficiency, provide code coverage information and generally improve the unit testing process. Included are a deep-dive into NCrunch and a TDD demonstration.",
