    "description": "In this course, we learn how to build Windows Runtime Components in C# for use in any Windows Store Application, whether the application is written in .NET, C++, or JavaScript. We cover what the Windows Runtime provides all applications. We learn the rules for creating new components in .NET. Finally, we spend time understanding what the projections look like into C++ and JavaScript.",
