    "description": "This course will teach you, the first principles of how to build platform style games using the Platform Game Starter Kit, and the underlying Jaws.Js, Howler.Js, Tween.JS and Ludus libraries. The starter kit gives you an on-rails approach to platform game development, so you can get up and running quickly with building your own game, and using JavaScript you can easily customize the existing games or start your own from scratch.",
