    "description": "Cloud platforms have gone mainstream, and Microsoft’s Windows Azure is among the most important options in this area. This course provides an introduction to Windows Azure, walking through each of its components. The goal is to provide a big-picture overview, explaining what the platform includes and when you would use each of its technologies.",
