    "description": "This course provides essential knowledge for IT Operations personnel to set up a basic installation of SQL Server on Windows Azure IaaS. Discussed are the different options for installing and configuring SQL Server in the Azure Cloud based upon your licensing and deployment requirements. The course explains how to configure supplemental data disks to improve your performance, and how to monitor and administer the SQL Server installation in Windows Azure IaaS.",
    "author": "Mike McKeown",
